text: Hun Manet (, ; born 20 October 1977) is a Cambodian politician and general. He has been the Prime Minister of Cambodia since 2023. He was in the Royal Cambodian Armed Forces (RCAF) as its deputy commander-in-chief and the commander of the Royal Cambodian Army. He is the oldest son of prime minister Hun Sen. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Cambodia Category:Current national leaders Category:Generals Category:Asian military people
